6
00:00:13.725 --> 00:00:15.960
Named entity recognition is

7
00:00:15.960 --> 00:00:17.730
a fast and efficient way to scan

8
00:00:17.730 --> 00:00:19.830
text for certain
kinds of information.

9
00:00:19.830 --> 00:00:24.300
NER systems locate and extract
named entities from text.

10
00:00:24.300 --> 00:00:26.610
Named entities can
be anything from

11
00:00:26.610 --> 00:00:30.645
a place to an organization
to a person's name.

12
00:00:30.645 --> 00:00:33.180
They can even be
times and dates.

13
00:00:33.180 --> 00:00:36.870
Let's discuss labels
